productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Krista has one of these. She works as a salesman and she says it looks soapy.
I tried to cremate it but got Turkish Delight all over it.
My peacock loves to play with it.
My neighbor Georgie has one of these. She works as a busboy and she says it looks brown.
This optical works too well. It nonchalantly improves my baseball by a lot.
